# UI/UX Designer User Stories - Music Band T-Shirt E-Commerce Store

## Overview

This document defines user stories specifically for the UI/UX Designer role in the Music Band T-Shirt E-Commerce Store project. These stories outline the design work required to create an intuitive, accessible, and engaging user experience that serves music fans, casual shoppers, gift buyers, and store administrators.

**Target User Personas**:
- Alex "The Passionate Fan" - Collection-focused power user
- Jamie "The Casual Shopper" - Convenience-driven occasional buyer
- Morgan "The Gift Buyer" - Efficiency-focused gift shopper
- Taylor "The Store Admin" - Operations-focused store manager

**Design Philosophy**: Create a music-first aesthetic that balances bold band imagery with clean, modern e-commerce functionality. Prioritize discoverability, speed, and emotional connection to music culture.

---

