#### Story UI-004.1: Order History Page Design

**As a** UI/UX Designer,  
**I want to** design an organized order history interface,  
**So that** users can easily find and review past purchases.

**Priority**: Must Have (MVP)  
**Estimated Effort**: 2 story points

