### Epic: P1-001 - Reviews & Ratings UI

#### Story P1-001.1: Product Reviews Interface

**As a** UI/UX Designer,  
**I want to** design a comprehensive product reviews system,  
**So that** customers can share experiences and make informed purchase decisions.

**Priority**: Should Have (Phase 1)  
**Estimated Effort**: 3 story points

**Acceptance Criteria**:

**Given** I am designing the reviews section on product detail page,  
**When** a user views product reviews,  
**Then** the interface must include:
- Reviews summary:
  - Average rating (large, 1-5 stars with decimal)
  - Total review count
  - Rating distribution bar chart (5★, 4★, 3★, 2★, 1★)
  - "Write a Review" CTA button
- Filters and sorting:
  - Filter by rating (All, 5★, 4★, 3★, 2★, 1★)
  - Sort by (Most Recent, Most Helpful, Highest Rating, Lowest Rating)
- Individual reviews:
  - Reviewer name (first name + initial or username)
  - Star rating
  - Review title (optional)
  - Review text
  - Review date
  - Verified purchase badge
  - Photos (if uploaded, thumbnail gallery)
  - Helpful votes ("X people found this helpful")
  - "Helpful" button (upvote)
- Pagination or "Load More" button
- Empty state ("Be the first to review this product")

**Given** I am designing the write review form,  
**When** a user submits a review,  
**Then** the interface must:
- Show modal or dedicated page
- Include fields:
  - Star rating selector (required, interactive)
  - Review title (optional)
  - Review text (required, 50-2000 characters, counter)
  - Photo upload (optional, up to 5 images)
  - "Submit Review" button
- Display character counter
- Show submission success message
- Require verified purchase (check order history)

**Design Deliverables**:
- Reviews section design (product detail page)
- Reviews summary component
- Individual review card component
- Write review modal/page design
- Review form with validation states
- Photo upload interface
- Helpful voting interaction
- Empty and loading states

