## Design Process & Workflow

### Design Sprint Structure

**Week 1-2: Design System & Foundations**
- Create design system and component library
- Define information architecture
- Map user flows

**Week 3-4: Core User Experience (Authentication, Catalog, Cart)**
- Design homepage and product pages
- Design authentication flows
- Design shopping cart and basic checkout

**Week 5-6: Checkout, Orders & Admin**
- Complete checkout flow
- Design order management pages
- Design admin dashboard

**Week 7-8: Refinement & Documentation**
- Iterate based on feedback
- Create design specifications for developers
- Prepare design handoff documentation

### Design Tools & Assets
- **Design Tool**: Figma (preferred) or Sketch
- **Prototyping**: Figma prototypes or InVision
- **Collaboration**: Figma comments, Slack, Jira
- **Handoff**: Zeplin or Figma Inspect mode
- **Version Control**: Figma version history
- **Icon Library**: Ant Design Icons, Heroicons, or custom
- **Stock Photos**: Unsplash, Pexels (music/band themed)
- **Illustrations**: Custom or unDraw/Storyset

### Design Quality Checklist

Before handoff, ensure:
- [ ] All screens designed for desktop (1440px), tablet (768px), mobile (375px)
- [ ] All interactive states shown (default, hover, focus, active, disabled, error)
- [ ] Color contrast meets WCAG 2.1 AA standards
- [ ] Touch targets minimum 44x44px
- [ ] Consistent spacing using 8px grid
- [ ] Typography hierarchy clear and consistent
- [ ] All copy proofread and finalized
- [ ] Loading states designed
- [ ] Empty states designed
- [ ] Error states designed with helpful messages
- [ ] Success confirmations designed
- [ ] Accessibility annotations provided
- [ ] Design specs documented (spacing, colors, typography)
- [ ] Assets exported and organized (icons, images, logos)
- [ ] Prototype created for key user flows
- [ ] Design reviewed and approved by stakeholders

---

## Success Metrics for UI/UX

### Usability Metrics
- **Task Completion Rate**: >90% users complete checkout successfully
- **Time on Task**: Average checkout time <3 minutes
- **Error Rate**: <5% of form submissions have validation errors
- **User Satisfaction**: System Usability Scale (SUS) score >80

### Engagement Metrics
- **Bounce Rate**: <40% on product pages
- **Pages per Session**: >4 pages
- **Session Duration**: >3 minutes average
- **Return Visitor Rate**: >30%

### Conversion Metrics
- **Conversion Rate**: >2.5% (MVP target)
- **Cart Abandonment Rate**: <70%
- **Add-to-Cart Rate**: >15% of product views
- **Wishlist Usage**: >10% of users create wishlists (Phase 1)

### Accessibility Metrics
- **WCAG 2.1 Compliance**: 100% AA compliance
- **Keyboard Navigation**: 100% of features accessible via keyboard
- **Screen Reader Compatibility**: All content accessible to NVDA/JAWS users

