**Notes for Developers**:
- All designs will be provided in Figma with detailed specifications
- Design system will include CSS variables/tokens for easy implementation
- Components designed to align with Ant Design 5+ for efficient development
- Accessibility requirements are mandatory, not optional
- Responsive designs prioritize mobile-first approach
- All interactive states must be implemented as designed
